And if you fucking don't know where the hell you called anyone a name,, well god forbid I be the first to point it out to you.  And god forbid also that I be the one to point out to you, how one person can call themselves one thing, but when another comes along and says the same thing - it's an insult.  If you don't see it, if you can't admit it, if you chose to be blind to it,,,,,,  wellllll..... <img src="images/smiles/eusa_silenced.gif" alt="eusa_silenced.gif" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
You are deragatory.  Period.   You don't like something, or you don't agree with someone, you pass judgement.  You were the first to point out to someone the title of this thread,,,,  yet you were also the first to take this thread and turn it into a personal attack.  And again, sweetie... if you can't see that...
<br />

